- âœ… All existing unit tests pass (293/293) - ensuring backward compatibility
- âœ… Added comprehensive tests for explicit interface functionality
- âœ… Verified all sensor implementations can be cast to `ISensor` and `IDeviceCapabilities`
- âœ… Confirmed delegation works correctly between explicit and public interface members

## Example Usage

```csharp
